ekgping - Electrocardiograph-like graphical and audible ping
---------------------------------------------------------

http://finalrewind.org/projects/ekgping/

Dependencies
------------

 * ping
 * perl >= 5.10
 * File::ShareDir
 * IPC::Run
 * Module::Build >= 0.36
 * SDL
 * Term::Size

Note that the Module::Build version shipped with perl 5.10 is too old for
ekgping.

Installation
------------

$ perl Build.PL
$ perl Build
$ sudo perl Build install
